1.1.name: wordpress/socialicons
1.1.description:
[PHP5 is required since version 2.70]

SocialIcons is a wordPress pugin that makes it easy to include social icons into your WordPress blog.

  • Widget
  • Shortcode
  • Search icons on Iconfinder.com and download to your blog (or site) /upload path
